rows.name: Ask San'luarb about mimeosomes.

rows.name: Discuss

rows.label: tev071101_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask San'luarb if anything is troubling him.

rows.label: tev071101_SEL1021
rows.name: Ask San'luarb about recent developments.

rows.label: tev071101_SEL1031
rows.name: Ask San'luarb what he intends to do next.

rows.label: tev071101_MSG0001
rows.name:
I understand that due to the complexity of their
construction, you are suffering from regular
shortages of parts.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071101_MSG0002
tev071101_MSG0003
rows.name:
I was told that the parts appeared unreliable,
as well as being quite...revolting.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071101_MSG0004
rows.name:
...Hmm? You aren't familiar with biotic components?
Well, to put it simply, they're extremely high-quality,
living parts.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071101_MSG0005
rows.name:
They are not dissimilar to the maggots of your native
Earth, except that they are programmed to move in
certain ways.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071101_MSG0010
rows.name:
I, along with my underling, Non'barac,
create components used by Orphean Technologies.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071101_MSG0011
rows.name:
Our inability to ensure a steady supply of the miranium
that we use as a primary material has been a source
of much vexation.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071101_MSG0012
rows.name:
You are a BLADE, are you not? I would ask that you
find a way to rapidly expand your FrontierNav in order
to improve miranium mining capacity.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071101_MSG0013
rows.name:
And please do hurryâ€”we have already used up our
entire miranium supply.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071101_MSG1001
rows.name:
My people do not naturally arrange ourselves into the
sorts of hierarchical structures that you humans seem
drawn to.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071101_MSG1002
rows.name:
Nevertheless, in an attempt to emulate a human-style
corporation, I adopted a leadership role with
Non'barac serving beneath me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071101_MSG1003
rows.name:
However, since Non'barac returned from her outside
research project, things have...changed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071101_MSG1004
rows.name:
She has since been handling the company's planning
and negotiating with the humans, while I have devoted
myself merely to crafting components.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071101_MSG1005
rows.name:
Could we have experienced a reversal of roles?
...Not that I would particularly mind if this were true.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071101_MSG1010
rows.name:
In the absence of the Ganglion, there is likely to be less
demand for armaments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071101_MSG1011
rows.name:
Therefore, it is imperative that we expand our line of
biotic devices into new product categories.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071101_MSG1012
rows.name:
I understand that you humans are repulsed by the
appearance of maggot-like creatures.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071101_MSG1013
rows.name:
But I assure you that while the products may appear to
be alive, they are made primarily from miranium,
and will not harm you even if touched directly.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071101_MSG1014
rows.name:
Perhaps one idea might be a product that allows you
to effectively shower without water. They could remove
filth from your bodies simply by undulating.[ST:wait ]
